    <cas:Sofa xmi:id="1" sofaNum="1" sofaID="_InitialView" mimeType="text" sofaString="An exhaus�ve nutri�on screening using mid upper arm circumference (MUAC) and Oedema for acute malnutri�on was conducted by Nutri�on Sector partners for 16 children of 6-59 months. Of the 16 children screened, the MUAC reading was no child (accessible areas) in the Red category, 5 were in the Yellow category and 11 were measured in the Green category. No case of Oedema was reported in the 2 LGAs that reports were received from. The results include no children from neighbouring countries. All children found with acute malnutri�on have been admi�ed in the treatment programme."/>
